58:08.542 --> 58:10.125
♪ Enough, enough, enough ♪

58:10.208 --> 58:12.208
♪ Is it ever gonna be enough? ♪

58:12.292 --> 58:14.125
♪ Is it ever gonna be enough? ♪

58:14.208 --> 58:17.042
I framed Ballister. I killed the queen.

58:17.125 --> 58:19.292
♪ Enough, enough, enough ♪

58:20.667 --> 58:22.583
-♪ Is it ever gonna be enough? ♪
-Oh!

58:23.167 --> 58:25.958
♪ Is it ever gonna be enough? ♪

58:26.042 --> 58:27.083
I killed the queen.

58:27.167 --> 58:28.417
Whoo-hoo-hoo!

58:28.958 --> 58:30.542
One question remains.

58:30.625 --> 58:32.417
Who's the real villain?

58:32.500 --> 58:34.750
Ahh.

